{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-docs-js","path":"/docs/xdebug.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"watch-the-video-tutorial\"><a href=\"#watch-the-video-tutorial\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Watch the video tutorial</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; \" > <div class=\"video\"> <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vCcT7TPv8lA\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen style=\" position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \"></iframe> </div> </div>\n<h2 id=\"setup\"><a href=\"#setup\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Setup</h2>\n<p>php with xdebug is can be set for local, by changing $PROJECT_IMAGE variable to <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">xdebug</code> in corresponding <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">.env</code> files, ensuring corrent docker image to be used.</p>\n<h2 id=\"debugger-settings-in-phpstorm-ide\"><a href=\"#debugger-settings-in-phpstorm-ide\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Debugger settings in PhpStorm IDE</h2>\n<p>Now to set the PhpStorm, go to:</p>\n<p><em>Preferences > Languages &#x26; Frameworks > PHP > Debug</em></p>\n<p>In this window check the following settings:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Xdebug section, set port 9111</li>\n<li>“Can accept external connections” is checked</li>\n<li>“Ignore external connections through unregistered server configurations” is checked</li>\n<li>Other settings is up to your preferences of the debugger</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Now we need to set up a server configuration, to map local files to remote application container, head to:</p>\n<p>_Languages &#x26; Frameworks > PHP > Debug > Servers__</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Add new configuration by clicking the <strong>+</strong> symbol</li>\n<li>Host: <localhost></li>\n<li>Port: 3001, which is default nginx port, try to avoid using varnish port and disable varnish in magento configuration during debug sessions</li>\n<li>Debugger: Xdebug</li>\n<li>And map your local <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">./src/</code> directory to remote <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">/var/www/public</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"setting-up-ip-alias\"><a href=\"#setting-up-ip-alias\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Setting up IP alias</h2>\n<p>To allow connections from container to debug console in PhpStorm you need to add following alias to you system, this setting is <strong>not</strong> persisted between restarts, update your env accordingly</p>\n<p><strong>Linux</strong></p>\n<p><code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">sudo ip address add 172.254.254.254/24 dev docker0</code></p>\n<p><strong>macOS</strong></p>\n<p><code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">sudo ifconfig en0 alias 172.254.254.254 255.255.255.0</code></p>\n<p>Now the configuration is complete, happy debugging!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Xdebug"},"fields":{"path":"content/docs/xdebug.md","slug":"/docs/xdebug.html"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/docs/xdebug.html"}}}